        <mxCell id="LknThsWM6TkXt3hYw1Ke-3" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="SET_EVEN&lt;div&gt;Ques -- Design a whatsapp system with proper following requirements&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.User Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.Chat Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.Group Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimise the chat service for handling the millions of request.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Specify the type of connection used in the design.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Determine how the dealing will be done for Last Seen functionality&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Implement CDC Pipeline in the same architecture.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="180" width="500" x="200" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LknThsWM6TkXt3hYw1Ke-4" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Functional Requirements :&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.The user should be able to create/register a account.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.The user should be able to login into its account.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. The user should be able to send and receive messages on chat.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.The user should be able to send and recieve messages to and from group.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;&quot;&gt;5.System should support sending message in both texual as well as media messages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6.The user should be able to see the message seen receipts.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="140" width="500" x="200" y="450" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LknThsWM6TkXt3hYw1Ke-5" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Non Functional Requirements :&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. The system should be able to handle 1.5 million daily users&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. According to the CAP theorum&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Availability &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; Consistency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;in this case as&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The system should be available all the time as the user just might need to see the previous chats and not even send or recieve messages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;so a small amount of delay to send message is not a big deal.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. The latency should be&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;200 - 300ms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;4. The system should be reliable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="500" x="200" y="680" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LknThsWM6TkXt3hYw1Ke-6" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Entities&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.User&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.Message&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Server&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="500" x="200" y="950" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LknThsWM6TkXt3hYw1Ke-7" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="API Structure&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.Put API - This is used to send data to the database via chat message via user.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.Delete API - This is used to delete a data from the database be it message data or Users data&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Get API - This is used to retrive the data from the data base&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="500" x="200" y="1150" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
